author: kfogel
msg: (SVN_LIB_NEON): Discover Neon version by looking at neon/.version,
as suggested by Joe Orton in issue #2297.

author: lundblad
msg: Fix bug in FSFS that made copying a special kind of mixed revision WC
to an URL fail.  With input from ghudson.
When a path was replaced during a copy, it got assigned the old node ID in the
changes file, which led to an error later on.
* subversion/libsvn_fs_fs/tree.c (copy_helper): Invalidate the DAG node cache
